{"tid":1751533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當選民主派及本土派共同宣言！","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:50:48.000Z","uid":110351,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02893624016b1bd38fc6716ed3a4263ae71c0901","tid":1751533,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"當大家仲打緊飛緊飛機嘅時候<br />\n理大仲有手足打緊仗<br />\n仲有手足係醫院<br />\n仲有手足打緊官司<br />\n仲有仲有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">場仗仲未完！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次選舉唔係食人血饅頭<br />\n而係一個民意表態<br />\n所有今次當選嘅區議員都係受益<br />\n所以極需要有一個宣言<br />\n表明你哋當選之後唔會當手足係condom!<br />\n同時向世界宣示<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可！</strong></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9766362faef972d3048c805d5ee45f4781b0a89","tid":1751533,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"文宣手足出手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c7a1740594f0b6ec67b383773f6f49e63025e5","tid":1751533,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2066633b6b38581b3df3c1247055a037bf84a5bf","tid":1751533,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"用共同宣言去話畀全世界知 場仗仲未完！"},{"pid":"a7117ed223f0e5be439d560cfb32cd3709c5